pattern_2.text: It is easier to tell the super husky players compared to other sizes. It is also easier to make guesses about the size in comparison to the player shown previously. Some of my guesses were based off how much bigger or smaller the player was compared to the one shown previously. It was hard to tell which players were slender, because all of them seemed a bit husky in a way. The players had to be very slender for me to tell. It was also hard to remember the initial qualifications for slender or husky, so after a while it just became slender or husky compared to other players I had seen in the line-up instead of based off the original guidelines.
